snippet.title: ArmZ VR – Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming to Steam Early Access on March 28th 2019.

Wishlist now on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/952930/ArmZ_VR/

Think quick, but shoot quicker in this insanely dynamic wave shooter with a pinch of tactics, where you operate a huge battle mech. Defend the city gates at all costs or else doomed creatures from the bottom of the post-apocalyptic hell will tear you to pieces, break through the gates and wipe the last human habitats off the face of the earth.
